# Deploy: app projects joining deploy

Use when designing or editing an app that will be added to the deploy repo.

- Expose **backend on 8080** and **frontend on 80** in their Dockerfile/server config so they match the deploy port convention.
- Use image names (or tags) that can be set via `PROJECT_BACKEND_IMAGE` / `PROJECT_FRONTEND_IMAGE` in `.env.prod`.
